w-up\nphenomena, and global solutions for the b-equation, {\\it J. reine angew.\nMath.}, {\\bf 624} (2008)51--80.]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Nov 2009 21:28:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-19"}
